CHANGES: REPO                                                      2.0
=======================================================================

2.0   (X. September 2011)
This release is a complete rewrite of repo-update. The naming has been
changed to just repo, the programming language has been changed to C,
and many improvements have been made to the concept (hence the name
change).

_______________________________
1.4.1 (20. April 2011)
This release just adds a Zsh completion script for repo-update,
and does not change the functionality of repo-update at all.

Enhancements:
  - Added a Zsh completion script.

